{"tid":953593,"cid":5,"subCid":0,"title":"★玩鳩你！】蘋果“再次”發布iOS 12.1.2 或修復小型Bug","createTime":"2018-12-24T05:05:14.000Z","updateTime":"2018-12-24T06:50:04.000Z","uid":19454,"like":1,"dislike":0,"uniUserReply":6,"replies":[{"pid":"8ccf2d5aa8735e2a8cce16d8cee24f09631b2023","tid":953593,"uid":19454,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-12-24T05:05:14.000Z","msg":"不久前蘋果向用戶推送了iOS 12.1.2 的更新，而今天凌晨蘋果再次發布了一版新的iOS 12.1.2，之前發布的更新版本號為&ldquo;16C101&rdquo;，而今天發布的版本號則為&ldquo; 16C104&rdquo;。<br />\n<br />\n於蘋果為何發布這一版本的更新目前尚不清楚，值得一提的是新的iOS 12.1.2 只會推送給那些尚未升級到這一版本的用戶，之前已經升級到最新系統版本的用戶無需再次更新，外媒預計本次版本小更新只是修復了一些小Bug，並對系統作出了部分調整。<br />\n<br />\n<a href=\"https://www.feng.com/iPhone/news/2018-12-21/Apple-again-iOS-release-12.1.2-or-repair-small-bugs_700158.shtml\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fwww.feng.com%2FiPhone%2Fnews%2F2018-12-21%2FApple-again-iOS-release-12.1.2-or-repair-small-bugs_700158.shtml&d=BOTFg90aRdpsR6jSq54p9mi1w7%2FDyS2Kz%2BsYtkalU0Y%3D&h=07ff07ce\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">https://www.feng.com/iPhone/news/2018-12-21/Apple-again-iOS-release-12.1.2-or-repair-small-bugs_700158.shtml</a>"},{"pid":"ef68e71600c38c76eccdb1c6c377fa6889e8a226","tid":953593,"uid":19454,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-12-24T05:05:22.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/haha.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/haha.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/haha.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/haha.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/haha.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"1c4e029da5becbd99b0eab9954a879b5f36bd790","tid":953593,"uid":95,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-12-24T05:06:40.000Z","msg":"Apple回撚曬塘啦"},{"pid":"10549ce5b5836b0f87f5b3703be1cc913b5fe577","tid":953593,"uid":19454,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-12-24T05:06:42.000Z","msg":"玩夠未<img src=\"/assets/faces/xm/clown.gif\"